@@TJvImageListBox.Alignment
Summary
  Controls the horizontal placement of the text and images within the label.
Description
  Set Alignment to specify how the text and images of the items are justified within the list box.
  
  When Alignment is set to taCenter, images are displayed above the text, when Alignment is either
  taLeftJustify or taRightJustify, images are displayed on either side of the text.
  
  The height of items are automatically adjusted to make sure that the entire item is visible.

